menu "OTA Update"

    config OTA_API_KEY
        string "OTA API key (X-OTA-Key header)"
        default ""
        help
            Secret key required in the X-OTA-Key HTTP header to authorize
            firmware uploads via POST /api/ota. Set a unique value here so
            the same key works across machines without needing serial access.
            If left empty, a random key is generated on first boot and stored
            in NVS — retrieve it once from the serial boot log.

endmenu
